7
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:16,630
I'm going to be finished.

8
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,760
Why not

9
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,000
just go all the way and...

10
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:20,840
No rush.

11
00:00:22,110 --> 00:00:23,670
I'll go check tomorrow.

12
00:00:24,710 --> 00:00:27,280
If he shows mercy, that would be best.

13
00:00:28,630 --> 00:00:29,920
But what if he doesn't?

14
00:00:35,550 --> 00:00:36,710
If he won't,

15
00:00:44,190 --> 00:00:45,320
