19
00:01:01,440 --> 00:01:02,550
Please accept it.

20
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,150
You've got good taste.

21
00:01:07,670 --> 00:01:08,510
Tell me.

22
00:01:08,630 --> 00:01:09,840
